@WG-prioritization/alerts issue #64718 has been requested for prioritization.

Procedure

  • Priority?
  • Regression?
  • Notify people/groups?
  • Needs I-nominated?
I know it's labeled as unsound, but fork() really seems like an edge case ... maybe P-medium or P-high?
I don't think there's much we can do here given the comments on the issue
by the way, why had this issue resurfaced now? Maybe because of the linked NetBSD one?
I'll take a chance and assign P-medium based on the issue comments, I feel there is nothing actionable (unless a deeper discussion is involved). Feel free to correct!
